.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-REMOTE-BALANCE-STDDEV" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-remote-balance-stddev \- FEAT-2750 stddev of remote balance across channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-remote-balance-stddev
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the standard deviation of remote balance across channels (FEAT-2750).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBremote_balance_stddev_msat\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
